{"id":2692,"date":"2012-03-31T08:35:56","date_gmt":"2012-03-31T04:35:56","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=2692"},"modified":"2023-07-06T15:27:37","modified_gmt":"2023-07-06T11:27:37","slug":"tolerance-forgive-leniency","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/tolerance-forgive-leniency\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Leniency: May Allah forgive a lenient businessman"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>May Allah<\/strong>\u00a0<b>have mercy on a man who is lenient when selling, buying, and seeking repayment.<\/b>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2076<\/p>\n<p>Grade:<b><i>\u00a0Sahih\u00a0<\/i><\/b>(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650<\/span>\u00a0<span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5e